" зробити так, щоб ``i % j`` мав той самий знак, що і ``i``."

#: ../../faq/programming.rst:840
msgid ""
"There are few real use cases for ``i % j`` when ``j`` is negative.  When "
"``j`` is positive, there are many, and in virtually all of them it's more "
